==Introduction==
「我ニ追イツク敵機無シ」有名な無電を発した俊足の艦上偵察機「彩雲」。<br>
敵戦闘機の追随を許さない高速性能を誇る、高性能な艦上偵察機です。<br>
悪化した戦況の中、敵情偵察に海上へと飛び立ちました。<br>
ぜひ、提督の機動部隊の正規空母、その第4航空隊に配備してみてくださいね。

''"No Grumman could catch us" was the famous telegraph sent from this reconnaissance aircraft, Saiun. This reconnaissance aircraft boasts high-speed performance no enemy fighter can overtake. As the war deteriorated, this aircraft monitored enemy movements at sea. Please deploy the 4th Reconnaissance Squadron on Admiral's Carrier Task Force!''
